39#include <sys/cdefs.h>
40#ifndef lint
41__RCSID("$NetBSD: print-mobile.c,v 1.6 2017/02/05 04:05:05 spz Exp $");
42#endif
43
44/* \summary: IPv4 mobility printer */
45
46#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
47#include "config.h"
48#endif
49
50#include <netdissect-stdinc.h>
51
52#include "netdissect.h"
53#include "addrtoname.h"
54#include "extract.h"
55
56#define MOBILE_SIZE (8)
57
58struct mobile_ip {
59 uint16_t proto;
60 uint16_t hcheck;
61 uint32_t odst;
62 uint32_t osrc;
63};
64
65#define OSRC_PRES 0x0080 /* old source is present */
66
67/*
68 * Deencapsulate and print a mobile-tunneled IP datagram
69 */
70void
71mobile_print(netdissect_options *ndo, const u_char *bp, u_int length)
72{
73 const struct mobile_ip *mob;
74 struct cksum_vec vec[1];
75 u_short proto,crc;
76 u_char osp =0; /* old source address present */
77
78 mob = (const struct mobile_ip *)bp;
79
80 if (length < MOBILE_SIZE || !ND_TTEST(*mob)) {
81 ND_PRINT((ndo, "[|mobile]"));
82 return;
83 }
84 ND_PRINT((ndo, "mobile: "));
85
86 proto = EXTRACT_16BITS(&mob->proto);
87 crc = EXTRACT_16BITS(&mob->hcheck);
88 if (proto & OSRC_PRES) {
89 osp=1;
90 }
91
92 if (osp) {
93 ND_PRINT((ndo, "[S] "));
94 if (ndo->ndo_vflag)
95 ND_PRINT((ndo, "%s ", ipaddr_string(ndo, &mob->osrc)));
96 } else {
97 ND_PRINT((ndo, "[] "));
98 }
99 if (ndo->ndo_vflag) {
100 ND_PRINT((ndo, "> %s ", ipaddr_string(ndo, &mob->odst)));
101 ND_PRINT((ndo, "(oproto=%d)", proto>>8));
102 }
103 vec[0].ptr = (const uint8_t *)(const void *)mob;
104 vec[0].len = osp ? 12 : 8;
105 if (in_cksum(vec, 1)!=0) {
106 ND_PRINT((ndo, " (bad checksum %d)", crc));
107 }
108}
